      "description": "Leave squads. Body: { memberId, squadIds?: string[] }.  If squadIds is omitted or empty, the member is removed from every active squad they are in (active squads created in the last 24 hours only).  Removing a guest: when leaving one squad only and the member has guests (AnonymousUsers > 0), we remove one guest.  Bulk: when leaving multiple squads, the member (and all their guests) are removed from each squad.",
